In large non-aluminum bowl or resealable plastic bag, pour Lawry's(R) Havana Garlic Lime Marinade With Lime Juice over shrimp; toss to coat. Cover or close bag, and marinate in refrigerator about 30 minutes. Remove shrimp from Marinade; discarding Marinade. On skewers, alternately thread shrimp and onion. Grill or broil shrimp, turning once, until shrimp turn pink. Serve with lime and hot pepper sauce and, if desired, with hot cooked rice, orzo or linguine pasta.